Class TextFlattener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.contentmine.svg2xml.util.TextFlattener

  • public class TextFlattener
extends java.lang.Object
    "flattens" numbers and dates in text to canonical forms. Used for comparing strings which differ only be nunbers ands dates e.g. 25, 33, are both flattened to 00
